➜Semecard速卖通采购常见问题
http://www.sohu.com/a/428364286_115514	11786
<p><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201030/acc2fcf35e644ec991747624707549ca.jpeg" /></p>
<p><span>问题1：需要验证semecard（appeal）</span></p>
<p><span>解决方案：</span><span></span>按照要求提交相关信息（appeal）</p>
<p><span>Step1.</span><span></span>上传身份证的正反面</p>
<p><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201030/c5958d82a8944343bd9de0f9f9da429f.png" /></p>
<p><span>step2：</span><span></span>semecard的App上，截一张图：包含完整的卡号</p>
<p><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201030/e2009c8e493048f499747dc93bd12e4e.png" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
